resources.string: The app will display the name, campus and if you have paid the semester. The app will also display photo of your choosing. The app serves as student ID, and can be used as legitmasjon with public transport companies in Norway.
At first use the app must be connected to the Internet to download the information. This is stored locally and does not need to be online to use the app later.
E-CardHolder assumes no responsibility for any fines, abuse, etc.
